#: ../../../diffusion/api/cli.md:1
msgid "SGLang Diffusion CLI"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/api/cli.md:3
msgid ""
"Use the CLI for one-off generation with `sglang generate` or to start a "
"persistent HTTP server with `sglang serve`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/api/cli.md:5
msgid "Overlay repos for non-diffusers models"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/api/cli.md:7
msgid ""
"If `--model-path` points to a supported non-diffusers source repo, SGLang "
"can resolve it through a self-hosted overlay repo."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/api/cli.md:10
msgid ""
"SGLang first checks a built-in overlay registry. Concrete built-in mappings "
"can be added over time without changing the CLI surface."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/api/cli.md:12
msgid "Override example:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/api/cli.md:14
msgid ""
"export SGLANG_DIFFUSION_MODEL_OVERLAY_REGISTRY='{\n"
"  \"Wan-AI/Wan2.2-S2V-14B\": {\n"
"    \"overlay_repo_id\": \"your-org/Wan2.2-S2V-14B-overlay\",\n"
"    \"overlay_revision\": \"main\"\n"
"  }\n"
"}'\n"
"\n"
"sglang generate \\\n"
"  --model-path Wan-AI/Wan2.2-S2V-14B \\\n"
"  --config configs/wan_s2v.yaml\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/api/cli.md:27
msgid ""
"The overlay repo should be a complete diffusers-style/componentized repo"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/api/cli.md:29
msgid ""
"You can also pass the overlay repo itself as `--model-path` if it contains "
"`_overlay/overlay_manifest.json`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/api/cli.md:31
msgid "Notes:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/api/cli.md:32
msgid ""
"`SGLANG_DIFFUSION_MODEL_OVERLAY_REGISTRY` is only an optional override for "
"development and debugging. It accepts either a JSON object or a path to a "
"JSON file, and can extend or replace built-in entries for the current "
"process."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/api/cli.md:35
msgid "On the first load, SGLang will:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/api/cli.md:36
msgid "download overlay metadata from the overlay repo"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/api/cli.md:37
msgid "download the required files from the original source repo"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/api/cli.md:38
msgid ""
"materialize a local standard component repo under `~/.cache/sgl_diffusion/"
"materialized_models/`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/api/cli.md:39
msgid ""
"Later loads reuse the materialized local repo. The materialized repo is what "
"the runtime loads as a normal componentized model directory."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/api/cli.md:42
msgid "Quick Start"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/api/cli.md:44 ../../../diffusion/api/cli.md:132
msgid "Generate"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/api/cli.md:46
msgid ""
"sglang generate \\\n"
"  --model-path Qwen/Qwen-Image \\\n"
"  --prompt \"A beautiful sunset over the mountains\" \\\n"
"  --save-output\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/api/cli.md:53 ../../../diffusion/api/cli.md:156
msgid "Serve"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/api/cli.md:55
msgid ""
"sglang serve \\\n"
"  --model-path Wan-AI/Wan2.1-T2V-1.3B-Diffusers \\\n"
"  --num-gpus 4 \\\n"
"  --ulysses-degree 2 \\\n"
"  --ring-degree 2 \\\n"
"  --port 30010\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/api/cli.md:64
msgid ""
"For request and response examples, see [OpenAI-Compatible API](openai_api."
"md)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/api/cli.md:67
msgid ""
"Use `sglang generate --help` and `sglang serve --help` for the full argument "
"list. The CLI help output is the source of truth for exhaustive flags."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/api/cli.md:70
msgid "Common Options"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/api/cli.md:72
msgid "Model and runtime"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/api/cli.md:74
msgid "`--model-path {MODEL}`: model path or Hugging Face model ID"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/api/cli.md:75
msgid "`--lora-path {PATH}` and `--lora-nickname {NAME}`: load a LoRA adapter"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/api/cli.md:76
msgid "`--num-gpus {N}`: number of GPUs to use"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/api/cli.md:77
msgid "`--tp-size {N}`: tensor parallelism size, mainly for encoders"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/api/cli.md:78
msgid "`--sp-degree {N}`: sequence parallelism size"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/api/cli.md:79
msgid ""
"`--ulysses-degree {N}` and `--ring-degree {N}`: USP parallelism controls"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/api/cli.md:80
msgid ""
"`--attention-backend {BACKEND}`: attention backend for native SGLang "
"pipelines"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/api/cli.md:81
msgid "`--attention-backend-config {CONFIG}`: attention backend configuration"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/api/cli.md:83
msgid "Sampling and output"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/api/cli.md:85
msgid "`--prompt {PROMPT}` and `--negative-prompt {PROMPT}`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/api/cli.md:86
msgid "`--num-inference-steps {STEPS}` and `--seed {SEED}`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/api/cli.md:87
msgid ""
"`--height {HEIGHT}`, `--width {WIDTH}`, `--num-frames {N}`, `--fps {FPS}`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/api/cli.md:88
msgid ""
"`--output-path {PATH}`, `--output-file-name {NAME}`, `--save-output`, `--"
"return-frames`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/api/cli.md:90
msgid ""
"For frame interpolation and upscaling, see [Post-Processing](post_processing."
"md)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/api/cli.md:92
msgid "Quantized transformers"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/api/cli.md:94
msgid "For quantized transformer checkpoints, prefer:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/api/cli.md:96
msgid "`--model-path` for the base pipeline"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/api/cli.md:97
msgid ""
"`--transformer-path` for a quantized `transformers` transformer component "
"folder"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/api/cli.md:98
msgid ""
"`--transformer-weights-path` for a quantized safetensors file, directory, or "
"repo"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/api/cli.md:100
msgid ""
"See [Quantization](../quantization.md) for supported quantization families "
"and examples."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/api/cli.md:102
msgid "Configuration Files"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/api/cli.md:104
msgid ""
"Use `--config` to load JSON or YAML configuration. Command-line flags "
"override values from the config file."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/api/cli.md:106
msgid "sglang generate --config config.yaml\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/api/cli.md:110
msgid "Example:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/api/cli.md:112
msgid ""
"model_path: FastVideo/FastHunyuan-diffusers\n"
"prompt: A beautiful woman in a red dress walking down a street\n"
"output_path: outputs/\n"
"num_gpus: 2\n"
"sp_size: 2\n"
"tp_size: 1\n"
"num_frames: 45\n"
"height: 720\n"
"width: 1280\n"
"num_inference_steps: 6\n"
"seed: 1024\n"
"fps: 24\n"
"precision: bf16\n"
"vae_precision: fp16\n"
"vae_tiling: true\n"
"vae_sp: true\n"
"enable_torch_compile: false\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/api/cli.md:134
msgid ""
"`sglang generate` runs a single generation job and exits when the job "
"finishes."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/api/cli.md:136
msgid ""
"sglang generate \\\n"
"  --model-path Wan-AI/Wan2.2-T2V-A14B-Diffusers \\\n"
"  --text-encoder-cpu-offload \\\n"
"  --pin-cpu-memory \\\n"
"  --num-gpus 4 \\\n"
"  --ulysses-degree 2 \\\n"
"  --ring-degree 2 \\\n"
"  --prompt \"A curious raccoon\" \\\n"
"  --save-output \\\n"
"  --output-path outputs \\\n"
"  --output-file-name \"a-curious-raccoon.mp4\"\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/api/cli.md:151
msgid "HTTP server-only arguments are ignored by `sglang generate`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/api/cli.md:154
msgid ""
"For diffusers pipelines, Cache-DiT can be enabled with "
"`SGLANG_CACHE_DIT_ENABLED=true` or `--cache-dit-config`. See [Cache-DiT](../"
"performance/cache/cache_dit.md)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/api/cli.md:158
msgid ""
"`sglang serve` starts the HTTP server and keeps the model loaded for "
"repeated requests."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/api/cli.md:160
msgid ""
"sglang serve \\\n"
"  --model-path Wan-AI/Wan2.1-T2V-1.3B-Diffusers \\\n"
"  --text-encoder-cpu-offload \\\n"
"  --pin-cpu-memory \\\n"
"  --num-gpus 4 \\\n"
"  --ulysses-degree 2 \\\n"
"  --ring-degree 2 \\\n"
"  --port 30010\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/api/cli.md:171
msgid "Cloud Storage"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/api/cli.md:173
msgid ""
"SGLang Diffusion can upload generated images and videos to S3-compatible "
"object storage after generation."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/api/cli.md:175
msgid ""
"export SGLANG_CLOUD_STORAGE_TYPE=s3\n"
"export SGLANG_S3_BUCKET_NAME=my-bucket\n"
"export SGLANG_S3_ACCESS_KEY_ID=your-access-key\n"
"export SGLANG_S3_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY=your-secret-key\n"
"export SGLANG_S3_ENDPOINT_URL=https://minio.example.com\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/api/cli.md:183
msgid ""
"See [Environment Variables](../environment_variables.md) for the full set of "
"storage options."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/api/cli.md:185
msgid "Component Path Overrides"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/api/cli.md:187
msgid ""
"Override individual pipeline components such as `vae`, `transformer`, or "
"`text_encoder` with `--<component>-path`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/api/cli.md:189
msgid ""
"sglang serve \\\n"
"  --model-path black-forest-labs/FLUX.2-dev \\\n"
"  --vae-path fal/FLUX.2-Tiny-AutoEncoder\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/api/cli.md:195
msgid ""
"The component key must match the key in the model's `model_index.json`, and "
"the path must be either a Hugging Face repo ID or a complete component "
"directory."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/api/cli.md:197
msgid "Diffusers Backend"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/api/cli.md:199
msgid ""
"Use `--backend diffusers` to force vanilla diffusers pipelines when no "
"native SGLang implementation exists or when a model requires a custom "
"pipeline class."
msgstr ""

